thread.title: EastEnders

author: Fiona Flynn
title: EastEnders
text: Phil is back tonight as you can see but in a very bad way following his ordeal with Gavin. Before that though, Sharon is pretty much filing for divorce after all that's happened, while Kathy heads back to the Beale house and tries to explain herself to an angry Ben. She reveals about the blood she found, pushing Ben to breaking point as he forces her to also admit the truth to Jay. Elsewhere, Shabnam prepares the residency application for Jade, much to Dean's annoyance, while she also informs Kush the wedding has been pushed forward to next week. Eh, think you might have wanted to talk that over with your groom-to-be there first Shabs.
